{
  "stem": "490.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But all of a sudden, we found out that the other cities-- we could not, of course, we could not move from one city to another.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could not-- we could not have any connection with other people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we, we were told that some cities the people are just taken away, and they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] news came out that those people are being put away in camps, and they were held there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the beginning, we didn't know that they were exterminated, they were killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But sometimes, all of a sudden, we found out that people escaped from these trains, which they were taking them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were-- they told us that it is a system now that even if you don't work and if you're not [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] useful to them, they are going to your chances of surviving are very slim.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, of course, there were so many.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They started-- right away, they started to cut off the Jews, to make, to make a ghetto in the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Before, you lived in the whole city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And now, they-- all of a sudden, they said that they are going to take away a lot of those elderly people who did not work, they're going to take them to a Jewish city.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They're going to make Jewish cities, where all the Jews can live there in freedom and at ease.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yes, it was like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But in the meanwhile, they squeezed the city, the Jews from the old-- in just a few blocks, a fewer streets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So you were limited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They call it a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was policed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we realized that it's getting tighter and tighter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took away those elderly people.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
